{
  "id": "adv_event_2108_01_03",
  "title": "月のテンペストらしい夏",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見市",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Hoshimi City",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.03333333333333333,
      "endTime": 4.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あーっ！　やっぱり海はいいね～\nいかにも、夏って感じで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh! The sea is the best!\nIt just screams summer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "endTime": 11.900000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、ここに来て正解だよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yup‚ we were right to come here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "endTime": 15.671437406539916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "確かに夏は凄く感じられるんだけど……\n暑過ぎて、曲作りに集中出来ないんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It certainly feels very summery here‚ but…\nit’s too hot to focus on making the song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 23.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……新曲作りのヒントは海にある！\nって芽衣ちゃんが言うから、来てみましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right‚ “the hint for making the new song is in the sea!”\nas Mei-chan said…so here we are…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8,
      "endTime": 30.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "早く新曲のイメージを掴んで、曲作りを\n手配してもらわないといけないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to capture an image for the new song quickly‚\nand make arrangements for writing the new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.966666666666665,
      "endTime": 36.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、あそこでかき氷売ってる！\n芽衣食べたい！　みんなの分も買ってくるね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ they’re selling shaved ice over there!\nI want to eat some! I’ll go and buy some for all of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.63333333333333,
      "endTime": 44.00000000000001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6733.333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、芽衣、私達、遊びに来た訳じゃ――\nって、もういない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Mei‚ we didn’t actually come here to play…\nOh‚ she’s gone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2,
      "endTime": 50.18839843184859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ、琴乃ちゃん。今まで、ずっと\nお仕事だったから、少しくらいはいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well Kotono-chan‚ we were working for a long time until now‚\nso isn’t it okay to relax a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4,
      "endTime": 56.46666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。午前中はリフレッシュして\n午後から新曲のヒント探しに専念でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. We’ll get refreshed in the morning‚\nand then focus on looking for ideas for the new song in the afternoon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.666666666666664,
      "endTime": 63,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "甘い！　渚も沙季も甘いですわ！\nそんなことではトップアイドルになれませんわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Naive! Nagisa‚ Saki‚ you’re so naive!\nWe won’t get to be top idols if we keep doing this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2,
      "endTime": 70.10000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "あの麻奈様だって、オフなんてないくらいの\n過密スケジュールをこなしつつ、数々の名曲を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-sama had her schedule so packed‚ she never took\nany time off‚ and she wrote so many songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3,
      "endTime": 77.70479415627412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "はーい、かき氷買ってきたよ～\nみんな、好きなの取ってね！　早い者勝ちだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here it is! I bought shaved ice for everyone!\nEveryone take the kind you like! First come‚ first served!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9,
      "endTime": 84.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私はいちご味を！　しゃくしゃくしゃく！\nう～ん、冷たくて甘いですわ！　美味！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want strawberry flavor! *munch* *munch*\nMmmm‚ cold and sweet! Delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9,
      "endTime": 96.17079588744018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん、切り替え早いね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan‚ you change your stance so quickly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 99.55251709620157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "さっき言ってたことと矛盾してるじゃないですか\nもう！　仕方ないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doesn’t this contradict with what you were saying earlier?\nYou all just can’t be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.76666666666667,
      "endTime": 105.21497917175293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "しゃくしゃく、買ってきてしまったものはしゃくしゃく\nしょうがあり――っ、頭がキーンとしますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*munch munch* She bought it already *munch*\nanyways‚ so—Argh! My brain froze…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4,
      "endTime": 115.83110762057098,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cloth-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15833.333333333328
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "あははは！　慌てて食べるからだよ～\nすずにゃんは可愛いな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. That‘s what you get for gulping it down.\nYou’re so cute‚ Suzu-nyan~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 122.90354159673055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、頭を撫でるのはやめてくれません？\nあなたと私は一つしか違わないでしょう！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would you please stop patting me on the head?\nYou are only one year older than I am!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 129.33333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……二人とも遊んでないで\nそろそろ曲作りの相談を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ will you two quit playing around?\nWe need to get on with discussing the song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 134.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "相談は、これを食べながらでもいいよね？\nはい、琴乃ちゃんは月と同じ色のレモン味～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can we discuss it while we’re eating this?\nKotono-chan‚ you get the lemon flavored one‚ the same color as the moon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1,
      "endTime": 143.06229272989125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ、まったく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.23333333333332,
      "endTime": 146.33333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、夏を楽しむことも、必要かな？\nかき氷、もらうわ。……美味しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I guess we need to enjoy the summer somehow…?\nThanks for the shaved ice… It tastes good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 156.5666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "私は、メロンをもらうね\nうん、甘ーい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll have melon flavor.\nMmm‚ sweet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.76666666666668,
      "endTime": 162.88745104097856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "この青色のはなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s this blue one?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.1,
      "endTime": 165.00000002384186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、それブルーハワイだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s Blue Hawaii!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.2,
      "endTime": 167.77039575576782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "なんですのそれは？　初めて聞く名前ですわ！！\nどんな味なんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But what is it? I’ve never heard of it before.\nWhat does it taste like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 173.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、たぶんハワイ味？　南国的な？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ maybe it tastes of Hawaii? Something tropical?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 180.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
